column2: select sa.objid, sa.ra, sa.dec, sa.type, sa.cmodelmag_r-sa.extinction_r AS cmod_r_corr, sa.psfmag_u-sa.extinction_u AS psf_u_corr, sa.psfmag_g-sa.extinction_g AS psf_g_corr, sa.psfmag_r-sa.extinction_r AS psf_r_corr, sa.psfmag_i-sa.extinction_i AS psf_i_corr, sa.psfmag_z-sa.extinction_z AS psf_z_corr, w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2, w.w3mpro AS w3, w.w4mpro AS w4, xm.match_dist AS match_dist, pz.z, pz.zerr, pz.photoErrorClass into mydb.MyTable_photo from PhotoPrimary as sa JOIN wise_xmatch AS xm ON sa.objid = xm.sdss_objid JOIN wise_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr LEFT JOIN photoz as pz ON sa.objid = pz.objid WHERE   sa.clean=# and   sa.specObjID=# and   (sa.psfmag_u-sa.extinction_u < #) and   (sa.psfmag_g-sa.extinction_g < #) and   (sa.psfmag_r-sa.extinction_r < #) and   (sa.psfmag_i-sa.extinction_i < #) and   (sa.psfmag_z-sa.extinction_z < #) and   (sa.psfmag_u-sa.extinction_u > #) and   (sa.psfmag_g-sa.extinction_g > #) and   (sa.psfmag_r-sa.extinction_r > #) and   (sa.psfmag_i-sa.extinction_i > #) and   (sa.psfmag_z-sa.extinction_z > #) and   (sa.cmodelmag_r-sa.extinction_r <#) and   (sa.cmodelmag_r-sa.extinction_r >#) and   (w.w1mpro<#) and   (w.w2mpro<#) and   (w.w3mpro<#) and   (w.w4mpro<#) and   (w.w1mpro>#) and   (w.w2mpro>#) and   (w.w3mpro>#) and   (w.w4mpro>#) order by sa.objid
